        "action": "Make carers allowance payable to carers after they reach pensionable age.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I have cared for my husband for the last 18+years after he sustained a traumatic brain injury. I had to give up my full time job to do this and now I find that I am going to loose CA  when I  reach pensionable age which I feel is grossly unfair as I am still a full time carer.",
